Slide 3: Key Features

This slide highlights the core functionalities of your Device Health Monitoring & Trend Analysis Dashboard to give the audience a clear understanding of what it offers.

Content for Slide 3:

Title: Key Features

Bullet Points:
	1.	Real-Time Device Status Updates – Continuously monitors uptime and downtime.
	2.	Failure Detection – Identifies offline devices, displays them at the top of the dashboard, and flags them in red for immediate attention.
	3.	Daily Health Monitoring – Helps in generating daily device health reports.
	4.	Trend Analysis & Insights – Tracks long-term device performance (daily, weekly, monthly).
	5.	Downtime Trends Displayed in Table Format – Visual representation of downtime trends.
	6.	Proactive Maintenance Support – Identifies devices that need repair based on frequent failures.

